{
  "stem": "15694.11",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After a long while, we found the others were stopped for lunch or for some kind of something to eat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we are breathing easier now, we have a little rest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I couldn't sit down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I let myself drop onto sort of like a-- a little hill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And two minutes later, the command was given.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "March again.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was held up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And somehow, I was up again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Again, by my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And how he could stand it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But the first ones must have reached the-- the destination long ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we were in at-- you know, at the very end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And those weak ones always tried to be a step ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because the guard in the back made, already, noises of great impatience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we were he might shoot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because-- because you know, we were the last ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I heard him speak and I could imitate dialects, and his dialect then and try to imitate this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I said-- in a German dialect-- not long anymore, and we will be home by mother-- with mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And after that, he kept-- he didn't say anything, what that we were so slow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "On the contrary, when the other guards went fine, have a way, he started a conversation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I wouldn't have spoken about the conversation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But only because he came from a village, had never-- he knows what-- about Jews, but he had never known a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He knew Frankfurt, came from, but he had never heard of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What should I argue with him, tell him anything?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, night came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, there was a moment where I could have disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because left and right, there were sort of ditches.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
